          },
          "datePublished": "2024-06-14",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I had an amazing journey as a student at The Sanskaar Valley School, and now I am proud to work here as a teacher. The overall personality development I experienced during my time as a student was remarkable. My spoken language skills improved significantly, thanks to the excellent environment and support provided by the school.\n\nHaving worked in many schools, I can confidently say that the respect and dignity The Sanskaar Valley School offers to both students and employees is commendable. The school fosters a friendly environment, which contributes to their impressive staff retention rate. The teachers are happy working here, and this happiness translates into their teaching, motivating students to come to school regularly.\n\nThe Sanskaar Valley School truly stands out for its commitment to creating a positive and nurturing atmosphere for everyone involved.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
